Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:36.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1053,596)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.74,0:01:40.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:40.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.91,0:01:41.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:41.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.91,0:01:44.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,醒醒  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:44.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wake up, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.66,0:01:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要把我钱烧光了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're burning me money
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.38,0:01:50.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:50.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, what do we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, use this
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.48,0:02:12.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:12.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.82,0:02:20.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  来我办公室一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:20.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, come into me office
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.74,0:02:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是怎么了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.20,0:02:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这周已经是第四次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the fourth time this week
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你从烤架上刮下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had to scrape you off of something
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直在想别的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I've been thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要让你多去想工作的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need to get you thinking about work
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.29,0:02:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无意冒犯  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No offense, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.75,0:02:34.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直在考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:34.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I've been thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.75,0:02:36.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要放弃冷冰冰的工业生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:36.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about giving up my cold industrial life
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.67,0:02:38.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转而选择更加自然更加自由的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:38.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in favor of a more natural and free life
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,栖身于水母之间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,among the jellyfish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:46.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(327,522)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在野外绝对撑不过一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't last even one day in the wild
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.94,0:02:56.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的自然栖息地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:56.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your natural habitat
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的开阔牧场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your wide-open range
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些是你的琥珀色海浪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are your amber waves
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.12,0:03:03.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:03.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.95,0:03:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是由你支配的黄金权杖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your golden scepter with which you rule
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比你那些恶心的水母强多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's better than nasty old jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以撑得过一天的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can too last more than one day
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给他瞧好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show him
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.59,0:03:22.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:22.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会回来的  准没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll be back, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll be back
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你收下我的开罐器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to have my can opener
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.06,0:03:36.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为这份友情没有回报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:36.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I thought this friendship would never pay off
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定要给我这瓶蛋黄酱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to give me this mayonnaise?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.53,0:03:42.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:42.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all yours
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有这些旧电话簿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And these old phone books?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是你的了  老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All yours, old friend
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  还有一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, there is one more thing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你收下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to have
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(583,618)}可靠好朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可靠好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ol' reliable?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.55,0:04:05.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:05.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你在开跳蚤市场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, you having a garage sale?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.97,0:04:08.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:08.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要放弃我所有物质财产
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm giving up my material possessions
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去野外跟水母一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to live in the wild with the jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.64,0:04:14.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你这什么疯狂计划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:14.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, of all the crazy schemes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么会要跟水母一块生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why would you want to live among the jellyfish?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们又冷血又坏  没一个聪明的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're cold and mean and none too bright
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.94,0:04:21.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:21.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就想听到你这种回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's exactly the response
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would expect from someone
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还活在我过去那种虚假的生活里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who lives the sham of a life I once lived
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.58,0:04:28.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要证明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:28.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna prove
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.28,0:04:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要快乐根本不需要这些玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I don't need all this stuff to be happy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终有一天你们会醒悟  而来加入我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe someday you'll wise up and join me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.79,0:04:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个我用不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't be needing these
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他把裤子脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He took off his pants
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.22,0:04:45.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他一周时间回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:45.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give him a week
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他十一分钟就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give him 11 minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.10,0:04:51.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星好伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:51.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick sad
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:57.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(437,884)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.81,0:05:03.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:03.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm home
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟姐妹们  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brothers and sisters, wait for me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  我到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  我才刚到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I just got here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.29,0:05:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的水母本能告诉我要走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My jellyfish instincts tell me to go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That way
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the life
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向你嗡个好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buzz to you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天水流不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice current today
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the buzz?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  我是水母宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm JellyBob--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.12,0:05:51.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:51.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他来了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There he is, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.01,0:06:11.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,念台词
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:11.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say your line
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Why, thank you, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would love one
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Take patty'
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.44,0:06:22.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真可惜海绵宝宝不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:22.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad SpongeBob isn't here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些可是他的最爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are his favorites
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望他能回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure wish he'd come home
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咬一口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Take bite'"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't do it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我才不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I'm not coming home
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I miss you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy misses you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.46,0:06:45.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连章鱼哥都好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:45.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even Squidward misses you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm happy here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这里才是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my home now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.52,0:07:01.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:01.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody, I'm back
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像快掌握诀窍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'm getting the hang of this
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你不能当我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I can't have you as a friend
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.59,0:07:29.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就把你当猎物抓走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:29.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make you a trophy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.05,0:07:33.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我甚至还给你挑了个好罐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:33.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I even picked out this nice jar for you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(395,786)}海绵宝宝  朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  快回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, go home
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在是水母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a jellyfish now
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看得到你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can see you there
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是能看得到你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still see you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你放我壁炉架上一定很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to look good on my mantel
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们永远都是好朋友  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friends forever, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要抓到你了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got you now, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, no
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来只能这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So this is the way it's going to be
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你能快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope you're happy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  全都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's over
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续做水母的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to jellyfish matters
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.56,0:09:01.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:01.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的水母同胞要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My jellyfish brethren are returning
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  兄弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings, comrades
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当水母真的好有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being a jellyfish sure is fun
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm itchy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.91,0:09:58.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:58.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Itchy--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么会这么痒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why am I so itchy?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有毒的海胆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poison sea urchins
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.41,0:10:08.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:08.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Itch
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.92,0:10:14.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:14.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Itch
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,832)}裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:33.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1107,474)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.70,0:10:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我生活好  朋友也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had a great life and friends
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我却全都放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I gave all of that up
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.47,0:11:02.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(841,328)}欢迎回家
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys are the best
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我犯了个天大的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made a huge mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.56,0:11:07.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:07.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别哭了  吃个蟹黄堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit your blubbering and have a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.10,0:11:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明早第一件事就是要去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll see you at work first thing tomorrow morning
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  请你行行好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, do us all a favor
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能别这样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could we please stop this?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick itchy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回家的感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is great to be home
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.85,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(318,309)}相反日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:55.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
