Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz16.87\pos(389,744)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz16.87\pos(445,324)}编剧
