Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:18.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(815,848)}生日快乐
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日快乐  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy, happy birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吃生日蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday cake
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy, happy birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别上海马尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pin the tail on the sea horse
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.47,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自pin the tail on the donkey游戏\N蒙眼把驴尾巴钉到无尾驴图片上 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy, happy birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日快乐  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.23,0:12:34.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:34.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别干我不会去干的傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything I wouldn't do
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.61,0:12:37.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又长大了一岁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:37.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another year older
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.23,0:12:41.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天不是我生日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:41.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not my birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要从这搬出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm moving out of this neighborhood
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absolutely, Mr. Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.53,0:12:50.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以马上卖掉你家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:50.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can sell your home in a heartbeat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:50.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(463,308)}裤头村房产
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great news
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我要尽快搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I want to move as soon as possible
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.83,0:12:59.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要房子不闹线虫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:59.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As long as it's not infested with nematodes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者旁边没有烦人的邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or surrounded by troublesome neighbors
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诸如此类的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or something like that
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然  一个都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, there's none of that
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说邻居吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you say neighbors?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.55,0:13:06.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:06.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都数不清碰见过多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you how many times
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.51,0:13:11.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,房子被烂邻居害得卖不出去的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:11.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've seen a sale fall through because of bad neighbors
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.77,0:13:12.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:12.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neighbors
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总之  我明天就过去看房
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll be by tomorrow to check out the house
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到时候见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you then
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有他住隔壁  没人会买我房子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one will ever buy my house with him living next door
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好邻居该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever a good neighbor would do
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.69,0:13:25.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他都会按相反的来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:25.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he does the opposite
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相反
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Opposite
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.45,0:13:30.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相反
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:30.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Opposite
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.09,0:13:43.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:43.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么在打鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you playing the drum?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.30,0:13:45.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:45.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drum?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What drum?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这只是我的假发盒  看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is just my wig case, see?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阻截我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tackle me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你需要躺床上休息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you need bed rest
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会保护你的  直到你康复为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll keep you safe until you're well again
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不知道今天什么日子对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't know what day it is, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,星期三
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wednesday?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.61,0:14:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是相反日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, it's opposite day
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.45,0:14:14.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是从来没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:14.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may you never heard of it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是都错过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, have you been missing out
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相反日是一年当中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Opposite day is the one day of the year
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.96,0:14:20.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都会反着来的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:20.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you get to act different
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.42,0:14:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平常我古板又无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Normally I'm stuffy and boring
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.21,0:14:27.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但今天我呆傻又放肆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:27.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but today I'm silly and spontaneous
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人都知道相反日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does everybody know about opposite day?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是游戏  明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a game, get it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A game
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.81,0:14:37.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:37.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平常你又吵又讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Normally, you're really loud and annoying
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么今天你要怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so what are you going to be today?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静不烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet and out of the way
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.86,0:14:48.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:48.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要不就先来一手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you get a jump on it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  我恨相反日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, I hate opposite day
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.91,0:14:59.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:59.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not ready
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永别了  老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, chum
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And good-bye, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  今天是相反日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, it's opposite day
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.26,0:15:07.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:07.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走路  不快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Walk, don't run
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相反  相反
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Opposite, opposite
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要趴到床上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to crawl into bed
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整天什么都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and do nothing all day
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.73,0:15:25.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真可惜相反日就一年一次  对吧小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:25.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad it only comes once a year, huh, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你的节日精神在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, where's your holiday spirit?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Company
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我讨厌同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate company
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.58,0:15:36.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:36.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.08,0:15:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.25,0:15:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.12,0:15:39.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:39.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不想见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never want to see you again
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.75,0:15:51.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝再也不喜欢我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:51.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob doesn't like me anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我的死对头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're my worst enemy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.22,0:16:00.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你不能算不是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:16:00.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're not really not my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.73,0:16:03.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是相反日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:03.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just opposite day
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.60,0:16:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相反日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Opposite day?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've heard of that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.61,0:16:07.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:07.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有  是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, what is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是平常做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever you normally do
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天都按相反的来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,today you do the opposite
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我试试  我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me try, let me try
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.75,0:16:23.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:23.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.33,0:16:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, breathe
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.67,0:16:31.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相反不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:31.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not that opposite
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来给你示范
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me show you how to do it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错误做法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the wrong way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:42.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(825,922)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,星大派
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kcirtap yeh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了服我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pu evig I
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面对路马到要鸡小为因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Edis etisoppo eht ot teg ot
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.16,0:17:04.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说  要来帮我在家附近干点活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:04.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, "Want to help me do some work around the house
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死对头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,worst enemy?"
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.51,0:17:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快中午了都没看到海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nearly noon and not a peep from SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我几乎都后悔要搬走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm almost sorry I'm leaving
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:26.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1267,648)}易碎
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相反日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Opposite day
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相反日是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't opposite day
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.58,0:17:45.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你住你隔壁哪糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:45.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what's terrible living next to you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是史上最差的邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the worst neighbor in history
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.25,0:17:52.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚那是章鱼哥对我说过最好的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:52.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the nicest thing Squidward has ever said to me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是房产中介看到那团乱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If the real estate agent sees that mess
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这房子就卖不出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never sell this house
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相反日这天是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On opposite day it is
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快让开  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of the way, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.45,0:18:22.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把我家弄得一团乱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:22.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made my house a mess
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表示的就是清理干净
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which was making it clean
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,导致章鱼哥过来清理我庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which made Squidward clean my yard
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可那就表示他在弄乱庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that means he's messing it up
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.21,0:18:28.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但干净的反义词是肮脏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:28.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the opposite of clean is filth
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表示脏东西是干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which means filth is clean
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以章鱼哥真在给我庭院搞破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That means Squidward's really
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:31.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,making my yard a wreck
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可平常我庭院都我搞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'd normally wreck my own yard
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以章鱼哥现在是章鱼哥的相反
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:33.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which means Squidward's being
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:34.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the opposite of Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.76,0:18:35.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以他是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:35.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which means he's SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我全都明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I understand everything now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.64,0:18:42.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想当海绵宝宝的相反  就要当
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:42.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must be the opposite of SpongeBob by being
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也想相反
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to be opposite, too
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算相反了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, finally
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是章鱼哥  我是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Squidward, I'm Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.20,0:19:02.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:02.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单是样子像章鱼哥还不够相反
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not enough to look like Squidward to be opposite
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要表现得跟他一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have to act like him, too
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.46,0:19:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢吹竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I like playing the clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我整天都练啊练
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I practice and practice all day long
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,却一点长进也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I never get any better
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.21,0:19:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you try
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.96,0:19:17.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:17.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是章鱼哥  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Squidward, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是章鱼哥  我是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Squidward, I'm Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是章鱼哥  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Squidward, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先请  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After you, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用客气  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're quite welcome, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相反日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Opposite day
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下次怕不是跳崖日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next time, it's going to be "Go jump off a cliff" day
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(763,878)}裤头村房产
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.57,0:19:45.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:45.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.53,0:19:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来看房感觉更漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The house is even more beautiful in person
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.00,0:19:51.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  章
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:51.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mist
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tentacles?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  请进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, please come in
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's funny
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以为你要高得多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I pictured you being much taller
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  大家都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, everyone says that
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要卖房成功的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now if you want the sale to go through
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.01,0:20:06.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就要先跟我说说房子的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:03.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you've got to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all the positive things about your house
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,优点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Positive things--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相反日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Opposite day
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love to
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.48,0:20:13.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地板会响  屋顶漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:13.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The floor creaks, the roof leaks
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿堂风很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a terrible draft
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.11,0:20:19.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你电话里都没说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:19.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you didn't mention that on the phone
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我先说完
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please let me finish
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冬天很难熬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The winters are hard
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夏天又毒辣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The summers are brutal
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.87,0:20:28.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后院里头还有只吃人的野蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:28.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a wild man-eating clam in the backyard
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.54,0:20:30.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想看看我家其他地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:30.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you care to see the rest of my home?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.12,0:20:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  我不太确定我有没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not sure if I'm interested
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nonsense
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不接受否定的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't take no for an answer
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please follow me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.05,0:20:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我家最烂的房间  我的画廊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here's the worst room in the house, my gallery
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.60,0:20:50.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  这些画真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:50.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, this painting is very nice
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.77,0:20:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要向你介绍章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to introduce you to Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩都是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're both Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're both Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's done
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码海绵宝宝一直都很安静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least SpongeBob has been quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:11.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(801,902)}裤头村房产
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.70,0:21:13.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:13.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.83,0:21:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  我真的不想再听一首了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I really don't want to hear another one
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真的不想再听了  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really don't want to hear more, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hear you loud and clear
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.72,0:21:26.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:26.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.84,0:21:27.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离她远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:27.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away from her
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.39,0:21:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.10,0:21:33.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望这两个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:33.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope these two barnacle-heads
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没伤到你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,haven't harmed you in any way
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.31,0:21:37.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:37.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.27,0:21:39.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:39.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是把我当成什么傻子了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of fool do you take me for?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.49,0:21:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.40,0:21:47.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:47.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.37,0:21:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有没有别的章鱼哥我该认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are there any other Squidwards I should know about?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.54,0:21:55.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:55.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.04,0:21:58.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:58.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, please
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.38,0:21:59.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我房子怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:21:59.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about my house?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.09,0:22:01.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算只剩你一个章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:01.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't sell a house for you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.59,0:22:04.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也不会帮你卖房子的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:04.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you were the last Squidward on Earth
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.09,0:22:06.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:06.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.47,0:22:07.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:07.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.13,0:22:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.01,0:22:12.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:12.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你卖我房子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please sell my house
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.60,0:22:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.69,0:22:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你别走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.57,0:22:24.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相反日快乐  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:24.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy opposite day, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.48,0:22:26.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:26.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We hate you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来给你们瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me show you guys
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.99,0:22:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有多讨厌你们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how much I hate you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.25,0:22:40.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你有没有觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:40.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you ever feel
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.58,0:22:42.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥太喜欢我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:42.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that Squidward likes us too much?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.71,0:22:46.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相反日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:46.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy opposite day
